reviewText:
Track Listings
1)Do You Want Crying - Katrina & the Wave
2)With All My Might - Byron Cage
3)Drive - The Cars
4)Only When You Leave - Spandau Ballet
5)Stay Up Late - Talking Heads
6)Wouldn't It Be Good - Nik Kershaw
7)People Are People - Depeche Mode
8)This World - The Dream Academy
9)Thin Line Between Love and Hate -
10)Why - Bronski Beat
11)Wood Beez - Scritti Politti
12)The Reflex - Duran Duran
13)Relax - Frankie Goes to Hollywood
14)Sisters Are Doin' It for Themselves - Eurythmics

I was really excited about this 80's music DVD.  It has some great tracks on it (how often do you find Scritti Pollitti videos?!?!), but the video quality is pretty bad.  It looks like a 10th generation dupe of a VHS tape, pretty disappointing.  :(
